            </div>
        </article> {%- endcomment %}

        <article>
            <h3><a href="https://applytriangle.bandcamp.com/track/if-this-reaches-you"><cite>If this reaches you</cite></a></h3>
            
            <p>My piece <a href="https://applytriangle.bandcamp.com/track/if-this-reaches-you"><cite>If this reaches you</cite></a> is on Apply Triangle's 2024 album <a href="https://applytriangle.bandcamp.com/album/oxalis-triangularis-complete-volumes-1-3"><cite>Oxalis Triangularis</cite></a> &mdash; I was one of the composers selected in the group's <a href="https://applytriangle.com/call_for_scores_2020.html">call for scores</a>. The album is a 3-CD release, and my piece is on <a href="https://applytriangle.bandcamp.com/album/oxalis-triangularis-vol-2">volume 2</a>.</p>
            
            <p>Contemporary classical magazine <cite>I Care If You Listen</cite> did an <a href="https://icareifyoulisten.com/2024/04/5-questions-to-apply-triangle/">intervew</a> with the group, and described my piece as having
            <blockquote class="mediaQuote">...a retro-futuristic vibe with electronic samples from distorted fax machines, maritime radios and walkie-talkies...</blockquote>
            
            <p>I also wrote a <a href="/posts/2024/04/new-album-announcement/">blog post</a> about composing the piece.</p>
                
